# MarketplaceV3DirectListings.cancelListing property

Cancel Direct Listing

## Example

```javascript
// The listing ID of the direct listing you want to cancel
const listingId = 0;

await contract.directListings.cancelListing(listingId);
```

**Signature:**

```typescript
cancelListing: {
        (listingId: BigNumberish): Promise<Omit<{
            receipt: import("@ethersproject/abstract-provider").TransactionReceipt;
            data: () => Promise<unknown>;
        }, "data">>;
        prepare: (listingId: BigNumberish) => Promise<Transaction<Omit<{
            receipt: import("@ethersproject/abstract-provider").TransactionReceipt;
            data: () => Promise<unknown>;
        }, "data">>>;
    };
```

## Remarks

Cancel a direct listing on the marketplace
